*USER HELP*
To set the time that you get notified, use *time 13:00*. Use a 24 hour clock.
To set the frequency of notifications, use *frequency daily*. You can choose from _daily_, _weekly_, _every other day_ or _weekend_.
TIMEZONE *NOT IMPLEMENTED* - defaults to Europe/London
LISTS *NOT IMPLEMENTED* - defaults to 'In Progress', 'Next', 'Incoming Tasks', 'On Hold / Waiting'